----------File Storage (students.json)----------------

Students are stored in JSON format for persistence.
Example content:

[
    { 
    "id": "101", 
    "name": "Raveena", 
    "age": 22, 
    "department": "CSE", 
    "marks": { 
        "Maths": 90, 
        "Java": 89, 
        "Python": 87, 
        "English": 86 
    } 
}

]

